                       skos:definition "A designed function borne by petroleum production equipment whose realization constitutes the removal of dissolved or entrained gases from a liquid to reduce their concentration."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/DegassingProcess
copi:DegassingProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                      rdfs:label "degassing process"@en ,
                                 "processo de degaseificação"@pt-br ;
                      skos:definition "A planned process in which dissolved or entrained gases are removed from a liquid to reduce their concentration below a specified level."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/DehumidificationFunction
