                                   rdfs:subClassOf copi:COPI_0000035 ;
                                   rdfs:label "flow signal transmission process"@en ,
                                              "processo de transmissão de sinal de fluxo"@pt-br ;
                                   skos:definition "A signal transmission process in which a standardised signal representing a measured flow rate is transmitted to a remote control or monitoring system."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/FlowSwitchingFunction
