                        rdfs:label "fenômeno físico"@pt-br ,
                                   "physical phenomenon"@en ;
                        skos:definition "A process in which a physical phenomenon—such as a pressure wave, temperature gradient, or electromagnetic field—that participates in or is generated by a petroleum production process."@en .


