                          rdfs:label "função de lançamento de pig"@pt-br ,
                                     "pig launching function"@en ;
                          skos:definition "A designed function borne by petroleum production equipment whose realization constitutes the controlled introduction of a pipeline pig into a pipeline under operating pressure."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/PigLaunchingProcess
copi:PigLaunchingProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                         rdfs:label "pig launching process"@en ,
                                    "processo de lançamento de pig"@pt-br ;
                         skos:definition "A planned process in which a pipeline pig is introduced into a pipeline under operating pressure to perform internal cleaning, inspection, or product separation."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/PigReceivingFunction
copi:PigReceivingFunction rdf:type owl:Class ;
                          rdfs:subClassOf [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
