                    rdfs:label "elemento de sensoriamento"@pt-br ,
                               "sensing element"@en ;
                    skos:definition "A material artifact that constitutes a primary element that directly responds to a physical or chemical variable to generate a measurement signal in petroleum production instrumentation."@en .


