                   rdfs:label "enrolamento de estator"@pt-br ,
                              "stator winding"@en ;
                   skos:definition "A material artifact that constitutes the stationary winding of an electric motor or generator that produces or responds to the rotating magnetic field in petroleum production rotating electrical equipment."@en .


