                                "structural force"@en ;
                     skos:definition "A quality inhering in a material entity, constituting a force transmitted through a structural element of petroleum production equipment due to imposed loads."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/StructuralSupportFunction
copi:StructuralSupportFunction rdf:type owl:Class ;
                               rdfs:subClassOf [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                 owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000054> ;
                                                 owl:someValuesFrom copi:StructuralSupportProcess
                                               ] ,
                                               [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                 owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000054> ;
                                                 owl:allValuesFrom copi:StructuralSupportProcess
                                               ] ;
                               rdfs:label "função de suporte estrutural"@pt-br ,
                                          "structural support function"@en ;
                               skos:definition "A DesignedFunction that is realized in a StructuralSupportProcess and that consists in providing mechanical support, load distribution, or structural integrity within an engineered system through a flat, planar configuration."@en ;
                               annotation:naturalLanguageDefinition "A DesignedFunction that is realized in a StructuralSupportProcess and that consists in providing mechanical support, load distribution, or structural integrity within an engineered system through a flat, planar configuration."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/StructuralSupportProcess
copi:StructuralSupportProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                              rdfs:label "processo de suporte estrutural"@pt-br ,
                                         "structural support process"@en ;
                              skos:definition "A PlannedProcess in which a structural element bears loads, distributes forces, or maintains structural integrity within a system, typically through its geometric configuration and material properties."@en ;
                              annotation:naturalLanguageDefinition "A PlannedProcess in which a structural element bears loads, distributes forces, or maintains structural integrity within a system, typically through its geometric configuration and material properties."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/SubsurfaceAccessProcess
copi:SubsurfaceAccessProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                             rdfs:label "processo de acesso subsuperficial"@pt-br ,
                                        "subsurface access process"@en ;
                             skos:definition "A planned process in which access to subsurface formations is established and maintained through a wellbore to enable exploration, production, or injection activities."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/SubsurfaceResourceInteractionFunction
copi:SubsurfaceResourceInteractionFunction rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                           rdfs:subClassOf [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                             owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000054> ;
                                                             owl:someValuesFrom copi:SubsurfaceResourceInteractionProcess
                                                           ] ,
                                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                             owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000054> ;
                                                             owl:allValuesFrom copi:SubsurfaceResourceInteractionProcess
                                                           ] ;
                                           rdfs:label "função de interação com recursos subsuperficiais"@pt-br ,
                                                      "subsurface resource interaction function"@en ;
                                           skos:definition "A designed function borne by petroleum production equipment whose realization constitutes the controlled physical interaction with subsurface formations to enable exploration, drilling, completion, or production activities."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/SubsurfaceResourceInteractionProcess
copi:SubsurfaceResourceInteractionProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                          rdfs:label "processo de interação com recursos subsuperficiais"@pt-br ,
                                                     "subsurface resource interaction process"@en ;
                                          skos:definition "A planned process in which petroleum production equipment physically interacts with subsurface formations to enable drilling, completion, or production operations."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/SubsurfaceSafetyProcess
copi:SubsurfaceSafetyProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                             rdfs:subClassOf copi:COPI_0000034 ;
                             rdfs:label "processo de segurança subsuperficial"@pt-br ,
                                        "subsurface safety process"@en ;
                             skos:definition "A safety relief process in which the wellbore flow path is automatically closed by a downhole safety valve to prevent uncontrolled flow of reservoir fluids to surface."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/SuctionInlet
copi:SuctionInlet rdf:type owl:Class ;
                  rdfs:label "entrada de sucção"@pt-br ,
                             "suction inlet"@en ;
                  skos:definition "A material artifact that constitutes the inlet through which fluid is drawn into a pump or compressor under suction pressure in petroleum production equipment."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/SupportFunction
copi:SupportFunction rdf:type owl:Class ;
                     rdfs:subClassOf [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                       owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000054> ;
                                       owl:someValuesFrom copi:SupportingProcess
                                     ] ,
                                     [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                       owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000054> ;
                                       owl:allValuesFrom copi:SupportingProcess
                                     ] ;
                     rdfs:label "função de suporte"@pt-br ,
                                "support function"@en ;
                     skos:definition "A designed function borne by petroleum production equipment whose realization constitutes the bearing of mechanical loads from attached components or piping to maintain their position and structural integrity."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/SupportedElectricalCable
copi:SupportedElectricalCable rdf:type owl:Class ;
                              rdfs:label "cabo suportado elétrico"@pt-br ,
                                         "supported electrical cable"@en ;
                              skos:definition "A material artifact that constitutes an electrical cable that is mechanically supported and routed by cable support systems in a petroleum production installation."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/SupportedTubingString
copi:SupportedTubingString rdf:type owl:Class ;
                           rdfs:label "coluna suportado de coluna de produção"@pt-br ,
                                      "supported tubing string"@en ;
                           skos:definition "A material artifact that constitutes a downhole tubing string that is suspended and supported from the wellhead by a tubing hanger in a petroleum production well."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/SupportingProcess
copi:SupportingProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                       rdfs:label "processo de suporte"@pt-br ,
                                  "supporting process"@en ;
                       skos:definition "A planned process in which mechanical loads from attached components or piping are borne by a structural element to maintain their position and integrity."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/SuppressedDisturbance
copi:SuppressedDisturbance rdf:type owl:Class ;
                           rdfs:label "perturbação suprimido"@pt-br ,
                                      "suppressed disturbance"@en ;
                           skos:definition "A process in which an unwanted physical perturbation—vibration, noise, or pressure surge—that has been attenuated or eliminated by petroleum production equipment."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/SurfaceSafetyValve
copi:SurfaceSafetyValve rdf:type owl:Class ;
                        rdfs:label "surface safety valve"@en ,
                                   "válvula de superfície de segurança"@pt-br ;
                        skos:definition "A material artifact that constitutes a safety valve installed at the wellhead or surface flowline that automatically closes to prevent uncontrolled flow from the well."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/TemperatureIndicationProcess
copi:TemperatureIndicationProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                  rdfs:label "processo de indicação de temperatura"@pt-br ,
                                             "temperature indication process"@en ;
                                  skos:definition "A planned process in which the temperature of a process stream or equipment surface is measured and displayed locally or transmitted to a remote monitoring system."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/TemperatureMeasurementAndTransmissionProcess
copi:TemperatureMeasurementAndTransmissionProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                  rdfs:label "processo de medição e transmissão de temperatura"@pt-br ,
                                                             "temperature measurement and transmission process"@en ;
                                                  skos:definition "A planned process in which process temperature is measured and the corresponding signal transmitted to a remote control or monitoring system."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/TemperatureMeasurementFunction
copi:TemperatureMeasurementFunction rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                    rdfs:subClassOf [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                      owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000054> ;
                                                      owl:someValuesFrom copi:TemperatureMeasurementProcess
                                                    ] ,
                                                    [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                      owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000054> ;
                                                      owl:allValuesFrom copi:TemperatureMeasurementProcess
                                                    ] ;
                                    rdfs:label "função de medição de temperatura"@pt-br ,
                                               "temperature measurement function"@en ;
                                    skos:definition "A designed function borne by petroleum production equipment whose realization constitutes the measurement of the thermal state of a process stream or equipment surface and its expression as a quantitative value."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/TemperatureMeasurementProcess
copi:TemperatureMeasurementProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                   rdfs:label "processo de medição de temperatura"@pt-br ,
                                              "temperature measurement process"@en ;
                                   skos:definition "A planned process in which the thermal state of a process stream or equipment surface is determined and expressed as a quantitative value."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/TemperatureSensingElement
copi:TemperatureSensingElement rdf:type owl:Class ;
                               rdfs:label "elemento de temperatura de sensoriamento"@pt-br ,
                                          "temperature sensing element"@en ;
                               skos:definition "A material artifact that constitutes a primary sensing element—thermocouple, RTD, or thermistor—that responds to temperature to generate a measurable signal in petroleum production instrumentation."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/TemperatureSensingProcess
copi:TemperatureSensingProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                               rdfs:label "processo de sensoriamento de temperatura"@pt-br ,
                                          "temperature sensing process"@en ;
                               skos:definition "A planned process in which thermal energy is detected and converted into a measurable signal representing the temperature of a process stream or component."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/TemperatureSensorProtectionProcess
copi:TemperatureSensorProtectionProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                        rdfs:label "processo de proteção de sensor de temperatura"@pt-br ,
                                                   "temperature sensor protection process"@en ;
                                        skos:definition "A PlannedProcess in which a protective barrier shields a temperature sensing element from direct contact with the process medium while maintaining thermal conductivity to enable accurate temperature measurement."@en ;
                                        annotation:naturalLanguageDefinition "A PlannedProcess in which a protective barrier shields a temperature sensing element from direct contact with the process medium while maintaining thermal conductivity to enable accurate temperature measurement."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/TemperatureSignal
copi:TemperatureSignal rdf:type owl:Class ;
                       rdfs:label "sinal de temperatura"@pt-br ,
                                  "temperature signal"@en ;
                       skos:definition "A measurement information content entity constituting an electrical or pneumatic signal representing the temperature of a process stream or equipment surface in petroleum production equipment."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/ThermalEnergy
copi:ThermalEnergy rdf:type owl:Class ;
                   rdfs:label "energia térmico"@pt-br ,
                              "thermal energy"@en ;
                   skos:definition "A material artifact that constitutes thermal energy transferred between a process stream and heat exchange surfaces of petroleum production equipment."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/ThermalEnergyPortion
copi:ThermalEnergyPortion rdf:type owl:Class ;
                          rdfs:label "porção térmico de energia"@pt-br ,
                                     "thermal energy portion"@en ;
                          skos:definition "A material artifact that constitutes a quantity of thermal energy at a defined point in the heat transfer circuit of petroleum production equipment."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/ThermalExpansionAccommodationFunction
copi:ThermalExpansionAccommodationFunction rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                           rdfs:subClassOf [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                             owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000054> ;
                                                             owl:someValuesFrom copi:ThermalExpansionAccommodationProcess
                                                           ] ,
                                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                             owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000054> ;
                                                             owl:allValuesFrom copi:ThermalExpansionAccommodationProcess
                                                           ] ;
                                           rdfs:label "função de acomodação de expansão térmica"@pt-br ,
                                                      "thermal expansion accommodation function"@en ;
                                           skos:definition "A designed function borne by petroleum production equipment whose realization constitutes the absorption of dimensional changes in piping or structures caused by variations in process temperature."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/ThermalExpansionAccommodationProcess
copi:ThermalExpansionAccommodationProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                          rdfs:label "processo de acomodação de expansão térmica"@pt-br ,
                                                     "thermal expansion accommodation process"@en ;
                                          skos:definition "A planned process in which dimensional changes in piping or structures caused by variations in process temperature are absorbed without transmitting excessive stress to connected equipment."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/ThreePhaseSeparationFunction
copi:ThreePhaseSeparationFunction rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                  rdfs:subClassOf copi:COPI_0000195 ,
