                                                    owl:allValuesFrom copi:ThreePhaseSeparationProcess
                                                  ] ;
                                  rdfs:label "função de separação trifásica"@pt-br ,
                                             "three phase separation function"@en ;
                                  skos:definition "A separation function borne by petroleum production equipment whose realization constitutes the separation of a gas–liquid hydrocarbon–produced water mixture into three distinct phases by gravity and residence time."@en .


###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/ThreePhaseSeparationProcess
