###  https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/VibrationMeasurementAndTransmissionProcess
copi:VibrationMeasurementAndTransmissionProcess rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                rdfs:label "processo de medição e transmissão de vibração"@pt-br ,
                                                           "vibration measurement and transmission process"@en ;
                                                skos:definition "A planned process in which the amplitude or frequency of mechanical vibration is measured and the corresponding signal transmitted to a remote monitoring system."@en .


